  "snippet": "Peter Savodnik, Suzy Weiss, Freya Sanders, and Elliot Ackerman on the WHCD incident. Plus: Abigail Shrier on what a &#39;real man&#39; is. Kara Kennedy&#39;s case for letting teens smoke. And more. ͏ ͏",
